FIREWORKS HOT LINE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Huge July 4 fireworks displays are being offered in a number of communities in 
the county. For questions about fireworks in your area, call the Los Angeles 
County Fire Department's fireworks hot line, (800) 442-3883, from 9 a.m. to 5 
p.m. 
</P>
