history series, 7 a.m.-noon, 3-5 p.m., 9-11 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
MOVIES: "Johnny Tremain" tells the story of the American Revolution-era 
historical figure, 6-7:30 p.m. on the Disney Channel . . . Clifton Webb and 
