8-9:30 p.m. Disney Channel . . . "A More Perfect Union: America Becomes a 
Nation" dramatizes the events leading up to the signing of the Constitution, 
8-10 p.m. KOCE Channel 50, 9:30-11:30 p.m. KPBS Channel 15 and 10 p.m.-midnight 
KVCR Channel 24. LAUREN LIPTON 
</P>
