<TEXT>
<P>
Alex Stewart, who is scheduled to fight Tyson in September, knocked down Jaime 
Howe in the fifth round, then stopped him 32 seconds into the seventh round of 
a scheduled 10-round heavyweight fight in Monticello, N.Y. 
</P>
<P>
