dropped him 1:07 into the fifth with a straight right. Howe is 15-12-1. 
</P>
<P>
Stewart, ranked No. 4 by the World Boxing Assn. and No. 5 by the International 
Boxing Federation, suffered his only loss last year against Holyfield. 
