<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB; 
</P>
<P>
MAN VS. MICROCHIP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Despite many close calls but no cigar, I will try a $10 triple from Mandona, 
Princess Loy, Conifer and Saratogas Beauty in the fourth to Express It in the 
fifth to Exemplary Star and Magical Royalty in the sixth. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's Sunday Bankroll: $1,931 
</P>
<P>
Sunday's Loss: $60 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $1,871 
</P>
<P>
The computer, which had three profitable days out of four last week after 
reaching a low point of $1,309, sent a message: I TOUGHEN UP WHEN THE 
(MICRO)CHIPS ARE DOWN. 
</P>
<P>
Its bets today are $5 daily doubles on Alabob's Pleasure and Kamikaze in the 
first race to Delaware Maiden and Iron Traveller in the second race. Also, a 
$40 exacta on Classic Fame to Steinlen in the eighth race and a $20 exacta 
reversing the two. 
</P>
<P>
Computer's Sunday Bankroll: $1,431.50 
</P>
<P>
Sunday's Profit: $10 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $1,441.50 
</P>
