UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT; BILL OF RIGHTS; CENSORSHIP; OBSCENITY; FREEDOM 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070490-0110 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 242764 </DOCID>
