Top Fund-Raiser: Sunwest Bank in Tustin was recently named the top fund-raiser 
in Orange County's 1990 March of Dimes "WalkAmerica" event. The bank's 
employees collected $55,000, nearly $25,000 more than the second-place team, 
the bank said. WalkAmerica is an annual event designed to raise money for the 
prevention of birth defects. 
