<P>
July 4, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
RENNY HARLIN 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
